Third refill costs a nickel.

03:48.603 --> 03:51.026
Tip.

04:31.062 --> 04:34.657
<i>Let's go! On the pass.</i>

04:34.733 --> 04:37.703
<i>Gotcha. Fifteen.
Let's go. Come on!</i>

04:37.778 --> 04:40.076
<i>And raise 10,000.</i>

04:40.155 --> 04:45.412
<i>Twenty-five! Five! Ten!</i>

04:45.494 --> 04:47.872
Come on. Come on.
Fifteen.

04:47.954 --> 04:50.332
Hey, you guys have limits.

04:52.167 --> 04:54.090
High five.

04:57.297 --> 05:00.426
And raise 10,000.

05:00.509 --> 05:04.355
<i>Anybody up?
Twenty-five. Gotcha!</i>

05:04.429 --> 05:06.807
One-seven-five,
one-seven-five left.

05:06.890 --> 05:09.860
<i>Nobody wants to bet
against my hitter here, huh?</i>

05:09.935 --> 05:15.157
Nobody wants to bet? Might as well
sell tickets to the place here.

05:15.232 --> 05:18.452
Three on my side!
I got three. Right.

05:18.527 --> 05:20.655
<i>Ten. I got ten.
Oh, biggies.</i>

05:20.737 --> 05:23.081
<i>- Anybody?
- Fifteen!</i>

05:23.198 --> 05:26.623
I got 30.
Oh, ho. Real spenders we got here.

05:26.701 --> 05:29.045
<i>Real high rollers.</i>

05:29.120 --> 05:31.122
Ah, you had your chance.

05:31.206 --> 05:33.709
<i>Come on. Let's go.</i>

05:34.793 --> 05:36.545
We're ready over here.

05:36.628 --> 05:39.757
Just remember, anything goes but
no hittin' when somebody's down.

05:39.840 --> 05:42.935
- Yeah.
- Okay. Let 'em go.

05:43.051 --> 05:46.055
You want it? You want it? Yeah? Go get it.
I want it.

05:57.607 --> 06:00.827
Get in there! Get in there!
Hey! Okay, Chuck!

06:19.170 --> 06:21.093
Son of a bitch.

06:25.260 --> 06:27.729
All right.
Come on, Chuck boy. Get him.

06:29.097 --> 06:30.770
Get in there!

06:32.183 --> 06:34.527
<i>Get in there. Get him.</i>

06:34.603 --> 06:37.857
<i>Get in there!</i>

06:37.939 --> 06:40.362
Ohhh!

06:40.483 --> 06:42.201
Go get him!

06:42.277 --> 06:43.745
Come on! Go get him!

06:45.947 --> 06:49.121
You can get him, Chuck!
Come on! Take him now!

06:51.828 --> 06:54.877
Move in on him.
Move in!

07:01.630 --> 07:03.052
Yes! Yes!

07:26.947 --> 07:32.704
<i>Come on. Get up.
Come on. Come on. Get up.</i>

07:32.827 --> 07:35.956
<i>Come on. Come on Get up!
Come on. Get up!</i>

07:40.251 --> 07:42.970
<i>Get up, you chump!</i>

07:50.220 --> 07:53.645
Hey, listen. I think I can
do about six more of those.

07:56.351 --> 07:59.025
Yeah. And a couple
of lemons there.

08:23.461 --> 08:26.556
You can start anytime, pal.

08:26.631 --> 08:28.725
Chaney.

08:30.969 --> 08:33.063
So what?

08:33.138 --> 08:35.390
We could make some money.

08:35.472 --> 08:38.977
Right. Well,
I'm all ears, friend.

08:39.059 --> 08:41.779
That piece of business tonight.
You set it up?

08:41.895 --> 08:44.399
Happens all the time. Help yourself.
Thanks.

08:44.482 --> 08:48.073
Suppose you been down
the long, hard road.

08:48.099 --> 08:49.434
Who hasn't?

08:50.655 --> 08:53.329
<i>Jail?</i>
You a policeman?

08:54.617 --> 08:57.040
Just like to know where men
come from, that's all.

09:02.000 --> 09:05.880
You look a little past it.
Besides, I already got a hitter.

09:06.004 --> 09:07.375
Yeah. Yeah. I saw him.

09:07.401 --> 09:10.205
Aw, son of a bitch laid
down on me tonight.

09:10.258 --> 09:13.432
Look, friend.
Every town's got a bar,

09:13.511 --> 09:16.560
and the bar's got somebody who
thinks he's tough as a nickel steak.

09:16.639 --> 09:19.563
But they all come
to Speed for the do-re-mi.

09:19.642 --> 09:22.020
He's a bum,
I'm the one that loses.

09:24.606 --> 09:27.155
I don't want your dough.

09:28.943 --> 09:32.743
I got six bucks...
and nothin' else.

09:32.822 --> 09:35.792
You bet it.

09:40.288 --> 09:43.212
Well, well, well,
my old friend Speeds back...

09:43.291 --> 09:45.840
with another potential winner.

09:45.919 --> 09:48.468
Anybody want to bet this man?
<i>Not after last night.</i>

09:48.546 --> 09:50.548
Anybody?

09:50.632 --> 09:53.476
<i>I'll give two to one.</i>

09:54.469 --> 09:56.642
Three to one!

09:58.056 --> 10:01.811
Come on! Odds like that
do not come around every day.

10:04.270 --> 10:07.114
Guess you boys aren't
as slow as he is.

10:09.067 --> 10:13.197
Gives us 150 in the pot.
Gonna hold it?

10:13.279 --> 10:16.829
And I got another 1-5-0 for anybody
expects a repeat. What do I hear?

10:16.950 --> 10:18.873
Fifty.
Twenty.

10:18.952 --> 10:20.920
Got it. I'll take it all.
Anybody else?

10:21.037 --> 10:24.883
<i>- You're crazy!
- You got 15 more. You a bettin' man?</i>

10:24.999 --> 10:27.343
<i> Oh, wail a minute.</i>

10:27.418 --> 10:30.797
We got another six.
That's all we got.

10:30.880 --> 10:32.757
<i>I'll take all of it.</i>

10:32.841 --> 10:34.764
I did my part, pal.
He's all yours.

10:34.843 --> 10:37.062
<i>Hey, Pops, you're a little old
for this, ain't ya?</i>

10:37.137 --> 10:40.858
<i>Let's go. Let's go. Get
the fight going. Come on.</i>

11:20.555 --> 11:25.106
Like everything else in this world,
it takes money to make money.

11:25.185 --> 11:27.108
Here's your 12.

11:28.438 --> 11:31.442
Another ten just
to have some fun on.

11:31.524 --> 11:33.652
Work out our official
deal later, huh?

11:33.735 --> 11:36.363
Plenty more
where that came from.

11:36.446 --> 11:38.448
You don't have
to worry about that.

11:38.531 --> 11:43.503
Now.
New Orleans-

11:43.578 --> 11:46.127
Speed's comin' home.
A little taste?

11:48.833 --> 11:51.052
No?

12:21.991 --> 12:23.664
Hello, sugarplum.

12:23.743 --> 12:25.290
How'd it go, Speedy?

12:25.370 --> 12:26.997
Well, a rough start
but a fast finish.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.548
Uh-huh. How much?

12:28.623 --> 12:30.466
Even.
Oh, wonderful.

12:30.541 --> 12:33.090
Always be pleasant
around strangers, honey.

12:33.169 --> 12:37.049
This is Chaney. Gayleen
Schoonover, my permanent fiancÃ©e.

12:37.131 --> 12:39.179
I'm pleased to meet you,
Mr. Chaney.

12:39.300 --> 12:42.850
There she is. Let's go.
I'll just say good-bye right here.

12:42.929 --> 12:45.057
Wait a minute, pal.
We got some plans to make.

12:45.139 --> 12:48.143
I wanna feel my way around the city.

12:48.226 --> 12:52.151
- What about our partnership?
- I don't like to rush things.

12:52.230 --> 12:54.198
Jesus Christ!
What are you talking about?

12:54.274 --> 12:57.244
Always be pleasant
around strangers, Speed.

12:57.318 --> 12:59.571
Are we gonna see
you again, Mr. Chaney?

13:00.989 --> 13:02.991
I might turn up.

13:04.909 --> 13:07.788
<i>Don't forget now.
Number 11 Dauphine Street.</i>

13:07.870 --> 13:10.544
Who was that guy?

13:10.623 --> 13:14.673
I'll tell you who he was.
Money on the hoof.

13:31.185 --> 13:33.654
It looks a little rougher
than it really is,

13:33.730 --> 13:36.779
but you get a lot of sun
through that window.

13:36.858 --> 13:39.202
Fix the place up,
could be real nice.

13:40.695 --> 13:43.574
Got some furniture down in the
storage room you could use.

13:43.656 --> 13:46.956
- Nah, I like it the way it is.
- Buck and a half a week.

13:49.203 --> 13:52.002
<i>In advance.</i>

15:09.158 --> 15:11.331
Mind if I sit down?

15:19.794 --> 15:22.923
Would you like to talk or just sit?

15:25.842 --> 15:28.470
What's your name?

15:32.974 --> 15:34.897
Who you waitin' for?

15:34.976 --> 15:39.732
I'm waitin' for somebody to
buy me another cup of coffee.

15:39.814 --> 15:41.782
Have mine.

15:48.322 --> 15:50.290
You live around here?

15:52.326 --> 15:54.420
Didn't take ya long
to get around to that one.

15:54.495 --> 15:56.623
Thought maybe
I could walk you home.

15:57.790 --> 15:59.758
Not likely.

16:04.422 --> 16:07.926
Girl had two choices
in my hometown.

16:08.009 --> 16:12.230
Stay and be bored or move
out and take chances.

16:12.346 --> 16:15.145
How's your luck been runnin'?
How can you ask that?

16:15.224 --> 16:17.192
Look how good I'm livin'.

16:17.268 --> 16:19.236
Well, I've seen worse.

16:19.312 --> 16:21.861
That depends on what
you're looking for.

16:21.981 --> 16:22.886
How 'bout you?

16:22.912 --> 16:25.886
I don't look past the
next bend in the road.

16:25.985 --> 16:28.204
Want me to come in?
No.

16:28.279 --> 16:32.409
- You sure?
- It's not that easy.

16:32.492 --> 16:36.793
I got a husband in jail.
No job and no prospects.

16:36.871 --> 16:41.547
- I wasn't plannin' on botherin' ya.
- Oh? What was your plan?

16:44.212 --> 16:46.306
Maybe I'll see ya around.

17:17.203 --> 17:19.126
Jesus Christ!

17:22.415 --> 17:24.384
Come on. Get up.

17:24.460 --> 17:26.428
Babe!

17:31.634 --> 17:34.433
H-Hey, good to see you, pal.

17:34.512 --> 17:37.015
I'm mighty glad
you found time to stop by.

17:39.141 --> 17:43.567
Come on! Get things started right.
Don't mind Sleepin' Beauty here.

17:43.646 --> 17:46.866
She's not one to rush into the
day's work, are ya? Goddamn it.

17:46.941 --> 17:50.991
We got an important guest here. How 'bout
gettin' up and fixin' breakfast for us?

17:51.070 --> 17:54.665
- Mornin'.
- Christ on a crutch.

17:55.866 --> 17:58.369
Hey, so I suppose you want
to talk deal, huh?

17:59.912 --> 18:04.008
Well, we go 50-50 on all
scratch bets and expenses.

18:04.083 --> 18:07.303
All side bets, I keep 75 percent.
That's how it works.

18:07.378 --> 18:11.633
Sixty-forty in my favor on scratch,
side bets down the middle.

18:13.301 --> 18:16.646
I'm tellin' ya the goin' rate.
What's normal. Ask anybody.

18:16.721 --> 18:19.941
- We'll do things different.
- Why should we?

18:22.018 --> 18:24.817
Because right now, my friend,
you got a percentage of nothin'.

18:24.895 --> 18:29.776
That makes me even with you. I'm puttin'
up all the money. I take all the risks.

18:34.238 --> 18:39.586
All right. All right. All right.
We'll do it your way.

18:39.660 --> 18:45.167
Gayleen! What's a man have to do
to get some breakfast around here?

18:50.171 --> 18:53.345
I got a good feelin' 'bout this.
I think we'll make some real money.

18:53.424 --> 18:58.476
I've got a couple things in mind.
Set something up for you next week.

18:58.554 --> 19:01.933
Go in slow, quiet. Four or five
hundred dollars. Something like that.

19:02.016 --> 19:04.895
There's something I want you to know.
I only come down here to make some money.

19:05.019 --> 19:08.023
Well?
And to fill in some in-betweens.

19:08.147 --> 19:10.027
In-betweens?
Hell, that's no kind of livin'.

19:10.053 --> 19:10.846
Well, it suits me.

19:10.900 --> 19:14.120
When I get enough change
in my pocket, I'm gone.

19:40.930 --> 19:46.482
We just mark this one down to research.
Part of your education.

19:46.560 --> 19:50.736
I wanna have a long talk with
anybody bettin' against me.

19:50.815 --> 19:53.489
Listen. A hundred dollars
against Curly.

19:55.152 --> 19:58.998
- On a marker.
- Uh-uh. No markers.

20:00.408 --> 20:02.831
- Chick, boy, wha-
- Take it.

20:06.997 --> 20:09.341
Who else?

20:09.417 --> 20:12.136
Who's the smoothy over there?

20:13.796 --> 20:18.347
That's Chick Gandil.
One of the big money belts in town.

20:18.426 --> 20:22.021
Son of a bitch has
broken me out three times.

20:23.597 --> 20:26.350
He's the one we're gonna shake.

20:34.984 --> 20:37.703
Anybody?
Last call!

20:37.778 --> 20:40.372
Stay away from him.
Move fast. Jab him.

20:56.130 --> 20:57.256
Ohhh!

21:47.556 --> 21:51.106
Somebody help this kid up.

22:20.089 --> 22:23.719
That's why he's the best.

22:23.801 --> 22:27.476
Nobody ever beats him.
Not many want to try.

